definitions.definition: Any of a class of compounds of general formula R 1 R 2 C(OH)OR' (where R' is not H and R 1 or R 2 is often hydrogen).

main_definition: ( organic chemistry ) Any of a class of compounds of general formula R 1 R 2 C(OH)OR' (where R' is not H and R 1 or R 2 is often hydrogen).
